.228c.533.047 1.111.08 1.722.096 1.22.032 2.554-.016 3.798-.204 1.231-.192 2.343-.538 3.155-1.033.704-.411 1.914-1.565 3.38-3.145a77 77 0 0 0 2.227-2.69 80 80 0 0 0 2.201-3.1c.679-1.071 1.365-2.145 1.947-3.168a138 138 0 0 0 1.526-2.826c.817-1.675 1.322-2.806 1.322-2.806s-.748.495-1.905 1.23"></path></svg></div></div><div class="Mission-module__XpHcwq__numbersItem" style="opacity:0"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Mission-module__XpHcwq__numbersTitle">с 1999 года</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Mission-module__XpHcwq__numbersDescription">стабильно на рынке</p></div></div></div></section><section data-background="secondary" class="Section-module__X_CtsW__section"><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container Principles-module__u7B41G__wrapper"><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__contentWrapper"><h2 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading Principles-module__u7B41G__heading">Что нас объединяет</h2><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cards"><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__card"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="none"><path fill="#19871B" d="M9.177 6.83c3.775-3.773 9.898-3.773 13.673 0L32 16l-9.164 9.171c-3.775 3.772-9.897 3.772-13.672 0L0 16.001zm6.83 2.505A6.67 6.67 0 0 0 9.337 16a6.67 6.67 0 0 0 13.339 0 6.67 6.67 0 0 0-6.67-6.665m0 2.267A4.404 4.404 0 0 1 20.408 16a4.404 4.404 0 0 1-4.401 4.398A4.405 4.405 0 0 1 11.604 16a4.405 4.405 0 0 1 4.403-4.398"></path></svg><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextTitle">Открытая культура</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextDescription">Честны с собой и коллегами. Помогаем друг другу и умеем говорить спасибо</p></div></div><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__card"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="none"><path fill="#19871B" d="m17.69 0 3.016 9.333 9.96.002 1.06 3.257-8.052 5.847 3.058 9.405-2.77 2.013-7.982-5.798-7.984 5.798-2.769-2.013 3.057-9.405-8.052-5.847 1.06-3.257 9.961-.002L14.268 0z"></path></svg><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextTitle">Создаём ценность</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextDescription">Делаем то, что приносит пользу аудитории и клиентам</p></div></div><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__card"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="none"><path fill="#19871B" d="M21.992 2.667a2.118 2.118 0 0 1 2.044 2.667h5.297v7.953c-2.52 1.687-5.39 2.873-8.463 3.509a5.12 5.12 0 0 1-3.737 3.076v2.846c2.398.117 4.703.58 6.867 1.346v5.27H8v-5.269a24 24 0 0 1 6.867-1.346v-2.847a5.13 5.13 0 0 1-3.729-3.071c-3.074-.636-5.948-1.825-8.471-3.514V5.334h5.287a2.113 2.113 0 0 1 2.038-2.667zM4.933 7.601v4.437a21.6 21.6 0 0 0 5.501 2.29L8.578 7.6zm18.483 0-1.844 6.723a21.5 21.5 0 0 0 5.495-2.286V7.601z"></path></svg><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextTitle">Драйв</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextDescription">Тёплая атмосфера, любимое дело и чувство, что ты на своём месте</p></div></div><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__card"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="none"><path fill="#19871B" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M28 24.467a20.4 20.4 0 0 0-10.326 4.28 2.67 2.67 0 0 1-3.348 0A20.4 20.4 0 0 0 4 24.467v-4.573a26.2 26.2 0 0 1 12.007 4.453A26.2 26.2 0 0 1 28 19.893zm-14.302-21.8c1.027-1.773 3.59-1.773 4.616 0l8.712 15.08a28.35 28.35 0 0 0-11.02 3.934 28.35 28.35 0 0 0-11.019-3.934z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextTitle">Динамичность</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextDescription">Следим за технологиями, пробуем новое и первыми запускаем лучшее</p></div></div><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__card Principles-module__u7B41G__cardWide"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="none"><path fill="#19871B" d="m30.668 15.156-13.403 3.592c.708.14 1.37.555 1.782 1.269l3.069 5.317c1.028 1.777-.256 4-2.308 4h-6.141c-2.053 0-3.336-2.223-2.31-4l3.07-5.317c.151-.259.341-.47.546-.654L3.38 22.471l-.586-2.192 27.29-7.313zM8.462 5.323a2.677 2.677 0 0 1 3.266 1.887l1.38 5.15a2.677 2.677 0 0 1-1.886 3.266l-5.152 1.38a2.68 2.68 0 0 1-3.266-1.886l-1.38-5.15A2.676 2.676 0 0 1 3.31 6.704zm13.672-3.988a5.868 5.868 0 1 1-5.867 5.867 5.87 5.87 0 0 1 5.867-5.867"></path></svg><div class="Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextTitle">Готовность к изменениям</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Principles-module__u7B41G__cardTextDescription">Не боимся перемен: ищем лучший путь, открыты новому и не стоим на месте</p></div></div></div></div><div class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__videoWrapper"><video class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__video" poster="/assets/principles/poster-vertical.jpg" muted="" playsInline="" preload="none"></video><div class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__overlay"><div class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__controls"><button class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__button PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__buttonVolume"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 30 30"><path fill="#fff" d="M14 4.5c0-1.41-1.66-2.16-2.71-1.21L6.59 7.5H3c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v11c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3.59l4.7 4.21c1.05.95 2.71.2 2.71-1.21zM22.59 15l2.7-2.7a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41l-2.7 2.7-2.7-2.7a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41l2.7 2.7-2.7 2.7a.996.996 0 1 0 1.41 1.41l2.7-2.7 2.7 2.7a.996.996 0 1 0 1.41-1.41z"></path></svg></button><button class="PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__button PrinciplesVideo-module__vbtBbW__buttonPlayback"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 31 34"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 4.999C0 1.157 4.159-1.245 7.485.675l20.208 11.671c3.327 1.92 3.327 6.723 0 8.643L7.485 32.657C4.16 34.579 0 32.177 0 28.336z"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></section><section data-background="tertiary" class="Section-module__X_CtsW__section"><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container Atmosphere-module__cyq00G__wrapper"><h2 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading Atmosphere-module__cyq00G__heading">Больше чем работа</h2></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__root AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carousel"><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__viewport AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselContent"><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__container"><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Команда экспертов" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Команда экспертов</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">Больше 50 наших ребят каждый год выступают на конференциях и митапах. А ещё мы сами организуем мероприятия для сообщества</p></div></div></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Бонусы для своих" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Бонусы для своих</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">Программа лояльности для сотрудников — скидки на ипотеку, в онлайн-школе для детей, в фитнес-клубах, корпоративном кафе и ещё в 30 проектах партнёров</p></div></div></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Ламповая атмосфера" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Ламповая атмосфера</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">Работать, дружить и отдыхать вместе — наша традиция. Корпоративы, слёты, настолки, просто уютные посиделки — у нас всегда есть повод собраться</p></div></div></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Уютные офисы" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm4.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Уютные офисы</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">В наших офисах много света и зелени, комфортные рабочие места, переговорки и зоны для отдыха, а на кухне всегда найдётся что перекусить</p></div></div></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Спорт и отдых" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Спорт и отдых</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">Участвуем в забегах и соревнованиях, проводим собственные кибертурниры и вместе катаемся по горам</p></div></div></div><div class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__item AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselItem"><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__card"><img alt="Здоровье и забота" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardImage" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1920px) 50vw, (min-width: 1440px) 60vw, (min-width: 1024px) 70vw, (min-width: 745px) 80vw, 90vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fatmosphere%2Fatm6.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextWrapper"><h3 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextHeading">Здоровье и забота</h3><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__cardTextDescription">ДМС, онлайн-помощь врачей с первого дня, комната сна, приёмы специалистов и сдача анализов прямо в офисе, медицинский агент для сотрудников и родственников</p></div></div></div></div></div><button disabled="" class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__button Carousel-module__6pHamq__prev AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselArrow AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselArrowLeft" aria-label="Предыдущий слайд"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="none"><path fill="#000" d="M18.8 10.233 12.15 16.9c-.633.617-.184 1.7.7 1.7H35v2.834H12.816c-.883 0-1.333 1.066-.7 1.7l6.667 6.65-2 2L5 20 16.8 8.233z"></path></svg></button><button disabled="" class="Carousel-module__6pHamq__button Carousel-module__6pHamq__next AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselArrow AtmosphereCarousel-module__Aw1J-a__carouselArrowRight" aria-label="Следующий слайд"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="none"><path fill="#000" d="M35 20 23.2 31.783l-2-2 6.65-6.666c.633-.616.183-1.7-.7-1.7H5v-2.834h22.184c.883 0 1.332-1.066.7-1.7l-6.667-6.666 2-2z"></path></svg></button></div></section><section data-background="secondary" class="Section-module__X_CtsW__section Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__wrapper"><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container"><h2 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__heading">Почему у нас классно</h2></div><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cards"><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardIt"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="M12 1c6.08 0 11 4.92 11 11s-4.92 11-11 11S1 18.08 1 12 5.92 1 12 1"></path><path fill="#fff" d="m17.861 7-5.16 9c-.77 1.33-2.69 1.33-3.46 0l-2.3-4h1.96l2.07 3.6L15.95 7z"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">ИТ-компания</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Мы третьи в рейтинге ИТ-компаний России*, создаём AI-решения, делимся опытом на конференциях, ведём блог на Хабре и гордимся<!-- --> <a href="https://manifest.2gis.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-variant="primary" class="Link-module__9THmpG__link">нашим Манифестом</a>. У нас государственная ИТ-аккредитация и есть льготная ипотека</p><small data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardSmall">*Всероссийский рейтинг ИТ-работодателей 2025 года от Хабра и исследовательской компании «Экопси»</small></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardEducation"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="M12.133 25.334c1.56 0 2.947.746 3.867 1.88.92-1.134 2.307-1.88 3.867-1.88h10.8V27.6h-12.2c-.733 0-1.334.6-1.334 1.333v.4h-2.266v-.4c0-.733-.6-1.333-1.333-1.333h-12.2v-2.266zM8.666 2.667c2.147 0 4.227.306 6.2.84v20a23.8 23.8 0 0 0-6.2-.84c-2.56 0-5.026.413-7.333 1.146v-20a24.2 24.2 0 0 1 7.333-1.146m14.667 0c2.56 0 5.027.413 7.333 1.146v20a23.8 23.8 0 0 0-7.333-1.146 23.8 23.8 0 0 0-6.2.84v-20a23.8 23.8 0 0 1 6.2-.84"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">Обучение и рост</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Выбирай курсы в нашем учебном центре, посещай конференции и прокачивай навыки за счёт
компании</p></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardAtmosphere"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><g clip-path="url(#lightning_svg__a)"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="m28.267 3.79-6.575 10.876h3.998l1.839 2.366L15.5 32h-2.707l.09-.388L24.81 16.934h-2.844L9.638 32H6.933l3.197-13.334H5.333L8.532 1.333h17.825zM15.829 14.665h2.945L25.535 3.6h-2.934z"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="lightning_svg__a"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 0h32v32H0z"></path></clipPath></defs></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">Атмосфера и традиции</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Праздники, традиции, подарки и душевные встречи — мы ценим моменты, которые нас объединяют</p></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardSales"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="M24.334 2.667c2.749 0 5 2.25 5 5v16.667c0 2.749-2.251 5-5 5H7.667c-2.75 0-5-2.251-5-5V7.667c0-2.75 2.25-5 5-5zM21.534 16c-2.09 0-3.8 1.71-3.8 3.8v1.735c0 2.088 1.71 3.8 3.8 3.8s3.8-1.711 3.8-3.8V19.8c0-2.09-1.711-3.8-3.8-3.8m-10.321 9.334h2.502l7.072-18.667h-2.503zm11.853-2.268H20v-4.799h3.066zm-12.6-16.4c-2.088.001-3.8 1.712-3.8 3.8v1.736c0 2.088 1.712 3.8 3.8 3.8 2.09 0 3.801-1.711 3.801-3.8v-1.735c0-2.09-1.711-3.8-3.8-3.8M12 13.734H8.933v-4.8H12z"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">Скидки и бонусы</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Скидки, привилегии от партнёров и выгодные предложения, которые делают жизнь сотрудников комфортнее</p></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDms"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="M16 1.333c8.1 0 14.666 6.569 14.666 14.667C30.666 24.1 24.1 30.666 16 30.666S1.334 24.1 1.333 16 7.9 1.333 16 1.333m-8.94 16C8.21 21.183 11.782 24 16 24c4.219 0 7.79-2.816 8.94-6.667h-2.404c-1.056 2.578-3.584 4.4-6.536 4.4s-5.48-1.823-6.536-4.4zm5.606-6.667a2 2 0 0 0-2 2V14a2 2 0 0 0 4 0v-1.334a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m6.667 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2V14a2 2 0 0 0 4 0v-1.334a2 2 0 0 0-2-2"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">ДМС и забота</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Расширенная программа ДМС, поддержка врачей и психологов в офисах и онлайн — чтобы ты чувствовал себя уверенно</p></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardOffices"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="M18.397 2.667a2.67 2.67 0 0 1 2.667 2.667v21.733h2.267V8h1.723A31.85 31.85 0 0 1 28 21.404c0 1.935-.185 3.825-.516 5.663h1.85v2.267H2.667v-2.267H4V16a2.67 2.67 0 0 1 2.667-2.666h.715v13.733h2.266v-4.4h5.074V20.4H9.648v-2.134h5.074V16H9.648v-2.666h5.074v-2.267H9.648V8.933h5.074V6.667H9.648V5.334a2.66 2.66 0 0 1 2.375-2.638v-.03z"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">Офисы в 30 городах</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Москва, Санкт-Петербург, Новосибирск и ещё 30 городов России — чтобы ты мог работать в любой точке страны</p></div></div><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__card Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardSport"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 32"><path fill="#19AA1E" d="m5.28 2.667.882 3.288A23.85 23.85 0 0 1 16 2.787v13.339a23.8 23.8 0 0 0-6.673 1.643l3.097 11.565H9.812L2.667 2.667zM28 17.334c-3.472 0-6.76.757-9.734 2.088l.002-13.334A23.8 23.8 0 0 1 28 4z"></path></svg><div class="Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTextWrapper"><p data-slot="text" data-weight="semibold" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardTitle">Спорт</p><p data-slot="text" data-weight="regular" class="Text-module__YrZoGG__text Opportunities-module__qTFtgq__cardDescription">Бегаем марафоны и побеждаем в турнирах. Тренируемся прямо в офисе или в фитнес-клубах со специальными скидками</p></div></div></div></section><section data-background="tertiary" class="Section-module__X_CtsW__section"><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container Join-module__ikaPmW__container"><h2 data-slot="heading" data-weight="semibold" class="Heading-module__IjHC4q__heading Join-module__ikaPmW__heading">Присоединяйся к нам</h2><a class="Button-module__xDwtkW__button Join-module__ikaPmW__button" role="button" tabindex="0" data-slot="button" data-variant="primary" data-size="md" href="/vacancies">Смотреть вакансии</a><img alt="Путь к новым карьерным возможностям" loading="lazy" width="690" height="390" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Join-module__ikaPmW__image" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fjoin%2Fnavigator.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fjoin%2Fnavigator.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fjoin%2Fnavigator.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/&--></main><footer class="Footer-module__7mNlWq__rootWrapper"><div data-width="lg" class="Container-module__q0hZta__container Footer-module__7mNlWq__container"><div class="